{"id": 2609, "genre": 1000, "title": "你对现在的“自助服务”都有哪些不满意？", "description": "本以为是社恐福音可以实现“零交流”，没想到反而加剧了社恐。（题图来自：iStock ©️CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 12918, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181107114054nZXc3Bmb4uvRo58L.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-15T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4931, "title": "你对现在的“自助服务”都有哪些不满意？", "content": "日常生活中你对“自助服务”都有哪些不满意？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 309132, "content": "使用说明不清晰，试半天才发现正确的刷证件方式", "image": "img/option/option/20181107112056kBEL42wq0blMuDVf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 309134, "content": "自助点餐没个性化选项，有忌口还是得跟服务员说", "image": "img/option/option/20181107114149KWQEm840qedOnVHN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 309138, "content": "有了自助点单系统，店员更难喊过来了", "image": "img/option/option/20181107114344KBywQxITAv7UOb9X.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 309140, "content": "医院自助服务不齐全，有的自助有的人工更混乱", "image": "img/option/option/20181107114357eUMAHbVGla1BEfCJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 309141, "content": "地下停车场信号不好，自助付费半天刷不出", "image": "img/option/option/20181107115127qQcGvOsyNJSX1TkE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 309142, "content": "必须关注公众号才能使用，后续收到无数推送", "image": "img/option/option/20181107120106I7l6FjGPzY5iS2qw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 309146, "content": "网上买了电子票结果还是要现场换纸质票并人工检票", "image": "img/option/option/2018110712000771ZWKhC6fz9D2BRi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 309147, "content": "自助客服选项太少不能解决问题，还是得找人工服务", "image": "img/option/option/20181107113958KuH2f6z3IWVn0RU1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}